[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":211},["ShallowReactive",2],{"sanity-RXp6fvBEHhAm7cPW_PXkzJe4MLPxGM93lTtTMD1wfIk":3,"sanity-U1bFKmTNSz7L8QDtaRWr_9vzrcaDQ_ml7HeL5Sn8fJ0":24},{"data":4,"sourceMap":8},{"defaultTitle":5,"ogDescription":6,"ogImageUrl":7},"Hubtown Limited | Leading Real Estate Developer in India","Hubtown Limited (formerly known as Ackruti City Limited) is one of India’s leading real estate developers, with over four decades of experience developing residential and commercial spaces and IT parks across India. The company primarily focuses on the Mumbai Metropolitan Region, Pune, and Gujarat. Hubtown has successfully delivered over 45 million sq. ft. of real estate, with an additional 20 million sq. ft. currently under development and 10 million sq. ft. planned for upcoming projects.",null,{"documents":9,"paths":12,"mappings":15},[10],{"_id":11,"_type":11},"siteSettingsSchema",[13,14],"$['defaultTitle']","$['ogDescription']",{"$['defaultTitle']":16,"$['ogDescription']":21},{"source":17,"type":20},{"document":18,"path":18,"type":19},0,"documentValue","value",{"source":22,"type":20},{"document":18,"path":23,"type":19},1,{"data":25,"sourceMap":71},{"footerBody":26,"footerTitle":27,"heroSubtitle":28,"heroTitle":29,"listItems":30,"metaDescription":34,"metaTitle":35,"openings":7,"quotes":36,"splitCards":49,"splitInfoCenterItems":60,"splitInfoCenterLabel":64,"splitInfoLeftBody":65,"splitInfoLeftHeading":66,"splitInfoLeftTitle":67,"splitInfoRightBody":68,"splitInfoRightHeading":69,"splitInfoRightTitle":70},"For over 40 years, Hubtown has created some of India’s most innovative real estate developments, spanning across Residential, Commercial and Industrial projects. From the drawing board to reality, across all facets of society.","About Hubtown","Build more than buildings. Build the future.","Build Together",[31,32,33],"Futures","Communities","Experiences","Explore career opportunities at Hubtown Limited. Join a leading real estate developer in India and build your future across residential and commercial projects.","Hubtown Careers | Real Estate Jobs in India & Mumbai",[37,41,45],{"author":38,"role":39,"text":40},"Rajeevan Paramban","Executive Vice President Operations","My journey with Hubtown Limited began 30 years ago as a Junior Engineer. Today, I am proud to serve as Executive Vice President.\nGuided by strong principles, we treat every partner as an extension of our team. With a consistent focus on quality, innovation, and growth, Hubtown offers clear career paths and the opportunity to build something meaningful.",{"author":42,"role":43,"text":44},"Laxmikant K. Mukhedkar","Manager Operations","I joined the company in 2013 as a Junior Engineer and have grown into my current role as Manager.\nWith the opportunity to take on diverse roles, I’ve gained hands-on experience across operations. The support throughout my journey has helped me develop a strong foundation in quality, innovation, and leadership.",{"author":46,"role":47,"text":48},"Madhavi Degaonkar","Senior Manager Company Secretary","Reflecting on my 19-year journey with Hubtown Limited, I’ve had the opportunity to take on diverse assignments and continually grow.\nThe organization’s focus on work-life wellness has allowed me to build a fulfilling career while maintaining balance, making this a truly rewarding long-term journey.",{"card1Description":50,"card1Title":51,"card2Description":52,"card2Title":53,"card3Description":54,"card3Title":55,"card4Description":56,"card4Title":57,"description":58,"title":59},"At Hubtown, every square foot tells a story. Join us and be part of transforming ideas into iconic structures that define cities and improve lives.","Purpose","We are invested in your growth. With learning opportunities, mentorship, and challenging assignments, you’ll keep evolving—just like the spaces we build.","Growth","We are a close-knit team of doers, thinkers, and creators. At Hubtown, you’ll find a workplace that values collaboration, integrity, and mutual respect.","Teamwork","From site engineers to sales teams, every voice is valued here. We believe diverse perspectives lead to better outcomes—and more resilient communities.","Unity","Being an Industry Leader our vision is to be the creator of value and enduring experiences for customers and our partners, to build remarkable landmarks that resonate our brand values.","Work with us",[61,62,63],"Founded in 1989","Multidisciplinary","550+ Employees","Information Data","Together, they bring bold ideas to life — transforming skylines, redefining communities, and setting new standards for innovation. At Hubtown, our people are more than professionals; they are visionaries driven by purpose, collaboration, and the pursuit of excellence. Their passion shapes not only the buildings we create, but the future we imagine.","At Hubtown, the most talented engineers, designers, and thought leaders are shaping the future of real estate industry.","Vision","At Hubtown, impact is measured in thriving communities, sustainable futures, and lives transformed. Our work shapes the way people live, connect, and grow — creating value that endures for generations. This is more than real estate; it is a legacy of purpose and possibility.","What we create is not just space — it is the backdrop for lives, stories, and communities. Every design carries the power to transform daily experience and inspire a better way of living.","Impact",{"documents":72,"paths":75,"mappings":110},[73],{"_id":74,"_type":74},"careers",[76,77,78,79,80,81,82,83,84,85,86,87,88,89,90,91,92,93,94,95,96,97,98,99,100,101,102,103,104,105,106,107,108,109],"$['footerBody']","$['footerTitle']","$['heroSubtitle']","$['heroTitle']","$['listItems']","$['metaDescription']","$['metaTitle']","$['quotes'][?(@._key=='7b450b4a37bf')]['author']","$['quotes'][?(@._key=='7b450b4a37bf')]['role']","$['quotes'][?(@._key=='7b450b4a37bf')]['text']","$['quotes'][?(@._key=='91a7c47a9a28')]['author']","$['quotes'][?(@._key=='91a7c47a9a28')][